NNU 00876, adult male, collected at the Shiwandashan National Nature Reserve , Shangsi County , Guangxi , China ( 21°55'1.2"N , 107°54'10.8"E ;
elevation 512 m
), collected by Wei-Cai Chen on 18 June 2022
.
